# Caddy

- Download Caddy with all plugins: curl https://getcaddy.com | bash -s git,filemanager,cors,hugo,ipfilter,locale,mailout,minify,ratelimit,realip,search,upload
- Set systemd permissions: sudo setcap cap_net_bind_service=+ep /usr/local/bin/caddy &>/dev/null
- Generate new key: sudo -Hu caddy ssh-keygen -t rsa
